EXTRACTED VALUE: Sega Rally Revo, like its predecessors, is all about the thrill of flying around a track. [Nov 2007, p.73]
My hat is off to Eidos mainly for expanding the variety of games on the 360. That is always a good thing.
Naruto: Rise of the Ninja is not one of the best ninja games to hit the market, but it is one of the best anime-based games ever released.
A great game for anyone looking for a super-fast brawl.
